data.description: Welcome to Lake Vista Ranch, where this one-owner gem awaits! This immaculate property boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an office for remote work. Inside, a spacious game room awaits, perfect for family fun or entertaining, throughout, you'll find tasteful updates, including charming shiplap accents that add character to the home. Upgraded light fixtures, fans, and new stylish faucets bring a modern touch to every corner. The bright open floor plan is filled with natural light, thanks to abundant windows that create a warm and inviting atmosphere. Step outside onto the large deck that surrounds the inviting pool, providing plenty of space for lounging and outdoor gatherings. In the backyard, lush turf creates a comfortable space for pets and play. This well-updated property is a testament to one owner's care and attention to detail. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own in the sought-after Lake Vista Ranch community.
